description: You can convert WoT models to the Wavefront 3D Object format with the World of Tanks Model Converter script. The PRIMITIVES_PROCESSED and .VISUAL_PROCESSED files are required in order to create the .OBJ or .MTL file. You can also open the PRIMITIVES_PROCESSED file with the 3D Object Converter and convert it to more common 3D formats such as .STL , .DXF , or .3DS .
